{"description":"When {{java.sql.Connection}} is acquired by calling {{javax.sql.DataSource#getConnection()}} it is not considered open and issue will not be raised if it is not closed.\r\n\r\nAlso consider signature with credentials {{javax.sql.DataSource#getConnection(java.lang.String, java.lang.String)}} .\r\n\r\n{code}\r\nvoid test_dataSource(DataSource dataSource) throws SQLException {\r\n    Connection connection \u003d null;\r\n    try {\r\n      connection \u003d dataSource.getConnection(); // FN - issue expected\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n{code}\r\n\r\nSimilarly issue is not raised on {{ResultSet}} obtained from {{java.sql.PreparedStatement#executeQuery}}\r\n\r\n{code}\r\nPreparedStatement preparedStatement \u003d connection.prepareStatement(\"SELECT\");\r\nResultSet result \u003d preparedStatement.executeQuery(); // FN - issue expected ResultSet should be closed\r\n{code}","component":"SonarJava","component_version":"4.11"}